feat: Add new layouts and pages for various mental health toolkits
- Implemented layout and page components for behavioral activation activities, checklists toolkit, journaling prompts, and self-compassion and self-esteem practices. - Enhanced existing pages for breathing techniques, cognitive behavioral therapy exercises, communication tools, emotional regulation toolkit, fitness toolkit, mindfulness practices, nutrition tools, progressive muscle relaxation guides, resilience toolkit, and leadership tools by removing unnecessary width classes. - Introduced context provider for tool information across new layouts to manage state and provide relevant data to child components. - Added loading states and error handling for data fetching in checklist and journaling prompt pages. - Removed outdated journaling tools page.
Add JournalPrompts interface to define structure for journaling prompts

Add journaling prompts for self-discovery, mindfulness, morning mindset, overcoming fears, resilience, and self-compassion
- Introduced life purpose and self-discovery prompts to encourage reflection on personal values and passions. - Added mindfulness prompts to enhance present-moment awareness and emotional acceptance. - Created morning mindset prompts to set positive intentions and cultivate gratitude at the start of the day. - Developed prompts for overcoming fear and limiting beliefs, focusing on reframing perspectives and taking actionable steps. - Included resilience journaling prompts to reflect on past challenges and build emotional strength. - Established self-compassion prompts to foster kindness and acceptance towards oneself.

Add various checklists for mental health support, including anxiety management, burnout prevention, daily self-care, depression support, emotional regulation, grounding techniques, healthy sleep hygiene, mindfulness practices, positive thinking, and social connection.
